{"tid":1627431,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【占星學】動物/寵物的星座!","createTime":"2019-10-05T15:51:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T04:33:46.000Z","uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"11a17be43fa92ea816938be710c447b0c80c9706","tid":1627431,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:51:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Qf8or0P4aZM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQf8or0P4aZM&d=AECyLZWdcqpY%2FGgvZN2GpMpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=12af0dcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Qf8or0P4aZM</a>"},{"pid":"b7c35f712341e3bc6fd0026574fa729a57822b07","tid":1627431,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:47:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">寵物兔是應該要被絕育</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">根據美國兔子協會(House Rabbit Society):</span><br />\n<br />\n1. 兔子是被捕獵動物(Prey animal), 是大自然內每個捕獵者(Predator)的目標, 狗吠聲、消防車叫聲、小孩尖叫、雷暴等也會嚇驚兔子, 所以不建議帶出外散步。兔子是全世界其中一個最多被棄養的動物(在美國排第3最多被棄養), 很多人將牠放生, 這樣會令兔子十分恐慌, 而且沒有覓食能力(寵物兔和野兔是不同), 有些人送給兔協, 但容納不到那麼龐大的數目。<br />\n<br />\n2. 絕育後會大大減少因荷爾蒙控制而霸地盤，不會隨地去廁所 (兔子是不需要訓練去廁所，只要廁所內有紙棉和乾草和夠大便可以, 建議用貓廁所)<br />\n<br />\n3. 荷爾蒙減少令攻擊性減少，更加溫馴和親人，也會活得更開心。如果想將2隻兔合養(做夫妻/好朋友)要先絕育才容易建立關係, 否則有機會打架！<br />\n<br />\n4. 兔子是很容易患上生殖器病動物，所以絕育會令到更健康和長壽！<br />\n<br />\n5. 減少過量繁殖(和棄養後所面對的困境)，繁殖得快和多。"},{"pid":"11775399c0ae12d5419fa6fb1d4f9ea3a5f9f925","tid":1627431,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:54:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有些人會問: 為什麼我在東, 我隻兔仔會面向著西?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n其實兔子<strong><ins>側面看某東西就代表正面看某東西</ins></strong>。牠們正前方和下方是盲點，除了這兩個盲點外，牠們幾乎可以看到360度。(所以有時食物在牠下巴下面睇唔到)&nbsp;<strong><ins>你在牠後面也會看到你</ins></strong>。兔子只有向著前方大約30度範圍，才可以有立體影像。牠們的脊椎就像軟骨那麼脆弱, 另外也有遠視。所以佢地唔係無視你，你是在他們視線範圍之內。<br />\n<br />\n兔子🐰是親人的群體性動物，但身體語言與其他動物不同，要做些研究才理解。(推介最底的3個網站)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">親人的動物：</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Maovq8Vz1LM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMaovq8Vz1LM&d=AECyLZWdcqpY%2FGgvZN2GpMpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=62db37f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Maovq8Vz1LM</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pyL0yEs-ka8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpyL0yEs-ka8&d=AECyLZWdcqpY%2FGgvZN2GpMpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=3d57c277\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pyL0yEs-ka8</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">兔子的行為解釋網站：</span><br />\n<br />\n香港兔協:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/knowledge8_ch.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2Fknowledge8_ch.php&d=AECyLZWdcqpY%2FGgvZN2GpMpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=b780dad4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/knowledge8_ch.php</a><br />\n<br />\n美國兔協 House Rabbit Society (教育網站):&nbsp;<a href=\"http://rabbit.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org&d=AECyLZWdcqpY%2FGgvZN2GpMpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=ba2e5ea0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbit.org</a><br />\n<br />\n詳盡身體語言解釋(喜怒哀樂):&nbsp;<a href=\"http://rabbitspeak.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbitspeak.com&d=AECyLZWdcqpY%2FGgvZN2GpMpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=627de019\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbitspeak.com</a>"},{"pid":"ecba5aa80e84e9d07b690968765315fdd0ce66a0","tid":1627431,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:33:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>兔子拚命地拯救一隻被困住的貓! 真感人! ☺</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n兔子是一種好心境平靜的動物，很多人覺得牠們咀嚼食物的聲音很治癒。如果你家的兔子有攻擊性，這不是牠的本性，而是後天環境和飼養方式影響。兔子亦被作為情緒和心靈支持動物(emotional support animal)，即是主人有醫生的證明，帶着小動物作伴，心靈才得到慰藉。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ydwwZtQyuiU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FydwwZtQyuiU&d=AECyLZWdcqpY%2FGgvZN2GpMpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=51d8bce1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ydwwZtQyuiU</a>"}]}